General.Name: Shih Kuen Plastics Co Ltd
General.Description: Shih-Kuen Plastics Co., Ltd. produces and supplies PVC plastic sheets and vinyl film. The company offers double polished PVC sheets, including clear and transparent colored; textured embossing PVC sheet, such as opaque textured, translucent, and semi-rigid textured; clear and colored laminated PVC sheets; and cold crack resistant and fire flame retardant PVC sheets. Its products are used in home and office supplies, construction and industrial, outdoor PVC waterproof covers, personal protective, and medical applications. The company was founded in 1986 and is based in Tainan City, Taiwan.
